QuestData.Title: Insurrection: March on Suramar
QuestData.Description: First Arcanist Thalyssra has sent word: the time has come to launch our assault on Suramar. The elven armies of the Horde, Alliance, Kirin Tor and Nightfallen are assembled.$b$BThey only await your arrival to begin their assault.$b$bReport to Shal'Aran and meet with First Arcanist Thalyssra and prepare for battle.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet with First Arcanist Thalyssra in Shal'Aran.
